OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDespite a
OL,6,Fsunny evening for Shetland cloud will
OL,7,Fbuild with some rain spreading north
OL,8,Ffrom, chance of thunder for Orkney.
OL,9,FSome brighter spells for Orkney by
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,13,Fweekend but chance of some bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells by afternoon, a warm day,
OL,15,Fperhaps some showers for Orkney later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
